Lerapo ke karolo e thata ya mmele e eleng bontlha bongwe ja mmele wa diphologolo tse di nang le mokokotlo. Marapo ke one a tshegetsang a bo a sireletsa dikarolo le dirwe tsa mmele, a dira metswako ya madi , masole a mmele, ke mabeelo a dikotla gape a fa mmele bokgoni ja go tsamaya. letsopa le le dirang lerapo ke mohuta o bokete wa go kopanyang. Marapo a mehuta e haroganeng ka popego le ka botona kgotsa bonyenyane gape a kopana ka bontsi le ka go farologana ga one ka popego go dira boteng le bokakontle jwa mmele. Ga a bokete mme a agegile gape ale thata, a thusa thata mo bokgoning jwa mmele. <span style="background-color: rgb(254, 252, 224);">letsopa le le agang lerapo le mehuta e mebedi </span> – lena le bokakontle jo bo thata le bokakoteng jo bo tshwaraganeng mme bona le diphatlhanayana (leshetla) go dira gore lerapo le itshwarelele thata. matsopa a mangwe a bonwang mo marapong ke moko, bokakontle, bokakoteng (leshetla), ditshika tsa mmele, ditshika tsa madi and mesifa.
